    <div class="text-block">
        <h3>Editing a Template</h3>
        <p>Step 2 of the creation process is to edit the template that has been selected. What was challenging about this part of the process was how to incorporate the various channel(s) into one editor. WIth MVP focusing on email and direct mail, I needed to come up with a elegant solution that allowed for easy toggling, but could also be scalable when other channels were going to be added.</p>
        <p>The end solution I came up with was to add a dynamic header to the top of the editor. Within this header I could have toggleable elements that would switch to the various channel specific editor view. </p>
    </div>

