    <div class="text-block">
        <p>When it came to editing the template itself there were some tight stipulations the client had for edit flexibility. The general premise was, upon creation the template author (internal GSM user) would stipulate which area of the template could be editable. This could be a text block or image block. When Bob at Toyota of Marin selects that template he is able to only change the text or image block to make slight adjustments based on his audience. He will not be able to adjust the layout or structure of the template itself.</p>
    </div>

