    <div class="text-block">
        <h3>Previewing &amp; Testing</h3>
        <p>When it came to previewing and testing the campaign, I utilized the header on top of the editor to house a dropdown button. For previewing I wanted to draw the users full attention to looking at their template. To accomplish that I made sure that when preview mode was clicked it entered into a full page modal experience. That way, the user could not accidently click out, reducing error state complexity. I also maintained the use of toggleable elements to switch between the different channel views. Different channels are going to have different preview states.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Image Block -->
    <div>
