    </div>

    <div class="text-block">
        <p>For sending a test message, I wanted to keep it simple and just utilized a simple centered modal. However, I still had to factor in how to send a test version of a direct mail template. It was concluded that a PDF would be the best solution. The user would have the option of including the PDF with each test through the use of some checkboxes.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
